channel.title: Webclient Doesn't connect
channel.description:
Hi guys, so today I was advertising and people tryed to get in my webclient. But it didnt work, and I got this error in the run console: [code] Connection from --------------ip--------------- null has logged out. Pass = null[/code] Then when he tried the client, it worked.
Can someone please tell my why my client works but not the webclient?
